item.title: Blonde Redhead - For The Damaged Coda - Ukulele Cheats
item.description: Play along video for the song For The Damaged Coda by Blonde Redhead from the channel Ukulele Cheats. Chords used in the song: A♯m6, Bdim, C5, Cm, Cm/D♯, Ddim, Fm, G, G7, G♯, G♯dim.
